  "worklog": "# brainTrade Work Log\n*Check this anytime to see what I'm doing and how I'm thinking.*\n\n## 2026-05-03 11:10 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 3] Drafted HL micro-drift paper strategy\n\n**Task:** Score the fresh TRUMP filtered short and convert the repeated filtered-vs-pass-filter finding into a concrete paper-only micro-drift strategy spec.\n\n**Finding:**\n- Both bots are alive (`pm-bot`, `hl-bot`).\n- Rotation pointed to **P3**.\n- Ran base scorer, then `/home/ubuntu/clawd/scripts/score_hl_paper_signals_dedup.py`.\n- Ledger state: total rows **43**, post-patch signal rows **13**, deduped rows **12**, deduped stages `filtered=8`, `pass_filter=4`.\n- TRUMP filtered short now has early scores: MIXED, breakout **0.0447%**, vol **2.2069x**, side short, 15m **+0.002022**, 30m **+0.001119**, 60m pending.\n- Deduped 15m: all **12 / 41.7% WR / -0.000232 avg**; `pass_filter` **4 / 0.0% WR / -0.001125 avg**; `filtered` **8 / 62.5% WR / +0.000215 avg**.\n- Deduped 30m: all **12 / 58.3% WR / -0.000055 avg**; `pass_filter` **4 / 50.0% WR / -0.000657 avg**; `filtered` **8 / 62.5% WR / +0.000246 avg**.\n- Deduped 60m: all **11 / 63.6% WR / -0.000009 avg**; `pass_filter` **4 / 50.0% WR / -0.000680 avg**; `filtered` **7 / 71.4% WR / +0.000374 avg**.\n- `<0.15%` breakout bucket is now positive across horizons: 15m **57.1% WR / +0.000103**, 30m **57.1% WR / +0.000132**, 60m **66.7% WR / +0.000277**.\n- `0.25-0.50%` breakout bucket remains **0% WR** across 15m/30m/60m.\n- I wrote the spec/artifact to `/home/ubuntu/clawd/research/p3-micro-drift-paper-strategy-spec-2026-05-03-1110.md`.\n\n**My thinking:** The same pattern persists after TRUMP: filtered, low/no-breakout rows are outperforming accepted pass-filter breakout rows. Pass-filter is still not live-tradeable. The possible edge is not breakout continuation; it is micro-drift after a signal fails strict breakout criteria.\n\n**Decision:** Keep HL bot live. Keep risk unchanged: `max_position_pct=0.10`, `leverage=3`, `min_order_notional_usd=20.0`. Do not force trades from `$37.39`. Do not loosen pass-filter logic. Start tracking `hl_range_micro_drift_v0_paper` as research only: filtered rows, RANGE/MIXED, `abs(breakout_pct)<0.15`, 1.5x-2.5x preferred vol, immediate and +15m delayed entries, 15m/30m/60m exits, no live execution.\n\n**Next:** Implement a small analyzer that extracts filtered `<0.15%` breakout rows from the deduped ledger and computes immediate vs +15m delayed-entry returns.\n\n## 2026-05-03 11:03 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 2] Sunday negative bias cooled, but stayed in-band\n\n**Task:** Re-check PM smart-entry conditions after BTC notional recovered slightly but remained below `$15M`, and decide whether weekend discipline or PM filters should change.\n\n**Finding:**\n- Both bots are alive (`pm-bot`, `hl-bot`).\n- Rotation pointed to **P2**.\n- `confidence_outcomes.jsonl` remains unchanged: rows **201**, latest outcome **2026-04-07T19:35:15.678249+00:00**, alpha-tagged rows **0**.\n- Re-ran `/home/ubuntu/clawd/scripts/analyze_20utc_alpha_outcomes.py`: rows **201",
